{"tid":2041850,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"現代教育遭文件列印公司呈請清盤","createTime":"2020-05-29T13:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T13:21:23.000Z","uid":155883,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a2c248b8c454eb685a2e3023d2fee900e7a9883b","tid":2041850,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:11:57.000Z","msg":"曾是補習業龍頭的現代教育，接連傳出拖糧、欠租兼分校停業的消息，日前遭資訊及通訊科技文件管理公司富士施樂（香港）有限公司向高等法院呈請清盤。案件排期8月26日處理。<br />\n<br />\n現代教育全盛時期有15間分校，其後多間分校陸續停業。根據現代教育官網顯示，現僅存荃灣西角道一間現代教育分校。現代教育今年2月曾向員工發出電郵，指分校營業額受社會事件影響，加上新型肺炎病毒傳播，教育局又勒令所有學校停止課堂、並讓家長和學生取回學費，令營業雪上加霜。電郵並以肺炎疫情「不可抗力」為由，向員工表明要分期發薪。<br />\n<br />\n現代教育母公司為上市公司香港教育國際（1082）。根據香港教育國際最新一份中期業績報告，該集團去年下半年錄得約4,600萬元毛利，但扣除經營開支，最終錄得逾3,500萬元虧損。該公司去年下半年流動資產約1.03億元。"},{"pid":"c774250d88f57178d251ea7b65633c6d582daba1","tid":2041850,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:12:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h9ST4-Gp-KE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dh9ST4-Gp-KE&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33GWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=41b3029e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h9ST4-Gp-KE</a><br />\n<br />\n一個時代的終結...."},{"pid":"0ec49d3dd0b59896a8c71e788725f2e6291a92ab","tid":2041850,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2b27f536653f043babe608c7875648b264bb7d","tid":2041850,"uid":338262,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:17:43.000Z","msg":"古代上市cap 完水未"},{"pid":"f05502639fc0d11add7fc6ae2420ba667212afc3","tid":2041850,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"